    "In the case of Mistral-7B, the adapter was merged with the CausalML model, facilitating prompt-based interaction and enabling the model to process and respond to natural language prompts.",
    "This adapted Mistral model, denoted as EconMistral AI, was subsequently evaluated using the same prompts employed in the zero-shot and few-shot learning experiments, ensuring consistency in evaluation across different training methodologies.",
    "Evaluation DatasetThe evaluation will use the F1 score matrix and an accuracy comparison.",
    "This new dataset was created from 500 random unseen paragraphs from the Oil Bulletin, the same source as the OM dataset.",
    "The master labelling dataset are labelled by the same experts who created the OM dataset."
